text: I seem to have lost when the requirements meetings are… I thought they were Monday, <@U0RSTB2DB> can you provide the info? Thanks

<@U0W7D64LC>:  They are indeed on Mondays. However, we are skipping the meeting next Monday as much of the WG will be at Consensus 2016.  You can find the meeting info in the Requirements WG link on the Wiki Home Page:  <https://github.com/hyperledger/hyperledger/wiki/Requirements-WG>

attachments.title: hyperledger/hyperledger
attachments.text: Hyperledger Project is a new Collaborative Project at The Linux Foundation. The technical community is just getting started and will be adding code to the repository in the coming weeks. Check hype...
